              <td><strong>Current Rating</strong></td>
              <td>Up to 100 A</td>
              <td>Typically 25 A – 100 A</td>
              <td>100 A up to 1600 A</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Sensing Mechanism</strong></td>
              <td>Bimetallic strip &amp; Solenoid</td>
              <td>Core Balance CT &amp; Relay</td>
